            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="42644509">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">德尔菲法。这个东西可以克服威权和盲从。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-03-27 10:19</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>德尔菲法。这个东西可以克服威权和盲从。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
