        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37005058/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37005058/" class="">集市模式的必要条件</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fleure/" class=" " title="红色有角F叔">红色有角F叔</a>
                (祖传老db 专治dba)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37005058">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">在软件设计上表现得聪明而有原创性，容易养成一个习惯——在应该保持软件健壮性和简单性的时候，你往往下意识把它弄得既华丽又复杂。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-01-17 20:43</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>在软件设计上表现得聪明而有原创性，容易养成一个习惯——在应该保持软件健壮性和简单性的时候，你往往下意识把它弄得既华丽又复杂。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
